languages.text: "Ты тоже мне не сразу открылась — мы оба поступили нечестно".
"You were hardly forthcoming yourself — neither of us have been completely honest."

languages.text: “你也没有对我透露你的真实身份，我们两个都有所隐瞒，你说呢？”
languages.original_text: "You were hardly forthcoming yourself — neither of us have been completely honest."

languages.text: «Usted tampoco compartió toda su información. Ninguna de las partes ha sido completamente honesta».
languages.original_text: "You were hardly forthcoming yourself — neither of us have been completely honest."

traits.locale_text: «Usted también me engañó a mí, ¿o acaso lo ha olvidado?».

languages.text: 「君は隠し事ばかりだった…お互いに心から正直に話したとは言えない」
languages.original_text: "You were hardly forthcoming yourself — neither of us have been completely honest."

traits.locale_text: 「君は隠し事ばかりだった…お互いに心から正直に話したとは言えない」

languages.text: "Ihr wart selbst nicht sonderlich zuvorkommend ... wir waren beide nicht ganz ehrlich."
languages.original_text: "You were hardly forthcoming yourself — neither of us have been completely honest."

traits.locale_text: "Ihr habt mich auch belogen, schon vergessen?"

languages.text: « Vous aussi, vous m'avez caché des choses. Sur ce plan-là, nous sommes quittes. »
languages.original_text: "You were hardly forthcoming yourself — neither of us have been completely honest."

traits.locale_text: « Vous aussi, vous m'avez menti, vous avez oublié ? »

languages.text: "Sen de pek açık sözlü değildin, ikimiz de tümüyle dürüst olmadık."
languages.original_text: "You were hardly forthcoming yourself — neither of us have been completely honest."
